    {
      "id": 1,
      "translated": "Here they are."
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "translated": "."
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "translated": "."
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "translated": "It's so good."
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "translated": "It really is."
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "translated": "That's how I feel."
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "translated": "Since I've already chosen my own career path, seeing the moment someone else makes their choice,"
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "translated": "even if it's just through an event story,"
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "translated": "there are definitely moments where you wonder if you're doing the right thing."
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "translated": "You definitely have those moments."
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "translated": "But if you can look back 10 or 20 years from now"
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "translated": "and feel glad that you made that choice back then,"
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "translated": "then I think that's a wonderful thing. And I believe effort is what makes that possible."
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "translated": "When it comes to things that require effort, I don't think there's such a thing as a 'right' or 'wrong' choice."
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "translated": "With a choice that requires effort, maybe in a year or two,"
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "translated": "you might have times where you regret it and think you shouldn't have done it."
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "translated": "But looking back after 10 or 20 years, I'm sure there are times when it all connects in the end."
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "translated": "You'll realize, 'If I hadn't done that then, I wouldn't be where I am now.'"
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "translated": "Even if you're in a different field, I'm sure you'll feel that way. For those of you working hard now,"
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "translated": "or if there's something you want to strive for, I hope this event story gives you the courage to keep going or make that decision. That's the kind of story it was."
    }
  ]
}

user_prompt:
[
  {
    "id": 0,
    "text": "ということで、、ここからはイラストについてお話ししていこうと思い。"
  },
  {
    "id": 1,
    "text": "ではお頼り紹介させて。"
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "text": "飯、飯さんからいただきましたお頼り。"
  },
  {
    "id": 3,
    "text": "ありがとうござい。"
  },
  {
    "id": 4,
    "text": "、佐藤、こんに。"
  },
  {
    "id": 5,
    "text": "、いつも楽しくプロセコをプレイさせてもらってい。"
  },
  {
    "id": 6,
    "text": "、今回の星4、特に瑞希イラストがとても良くて必死でガチャを、"
  },
  {
    "id": 7,
    "text": "手に入れまし。"
  },
  {
    "id": 8,
    "text": "今回のイラストもシークレットディスタンスや軽音曲の道はいずこ、どこ、"
  },
  {
    "id": 9,
    "text": "いずこ。"
  },
  {
    "id": 10,
    "text": "、、瑞希の特訓後イラストのようにトルソーの空間、、トルソっていうのは結構瑞希のイラストでよく出てくる、"
  },
  {
    "id": 11,
    "text": "マネキンじゃない、お洋服、こういう。"
  },
  {
    "id": 12,
    "text": "あのここに、ここに、。"
  },
  {
    "id": 13,
    "text": "、、、、。"
  },
  {
    "id": 14,
    "text": "ここに。"
  },
  {
    "id": 15,
    "text": "これトルソって言い。"
  },
  {
    "id": 16,
    "text": "ほどけぬ明日に手を伸ばし、トルソー。"
  },
  {
    "id": 17,
    "text": "、トルソーの空間に瑞希がいるイラストでし。"
  },
  {
    "id": 18,
    "text": "いつもは瑞希の暗い気持ちを表すものとなっていたトルソーの空間です、"
  },
  {
    "id": 19,
    "text": "今回は家族や、友達の温かさに触れて前を向いて、"
  },
  {
    "id": 20,
    "text": "、瑞希の晴れやかで明るい気持ちを表す空間になってい、瑞希の心境の変化を、"
  },
  {
    "id": 21,
    "text": "とても嬉しく思いまし。"
  },
  {
    "id": 22,
    "text": "こんなに素晴らしい、シナリオを作るスタッフ、またこれらに深みを持たせる、"
  },
  {
    "id": 23,
    "text": "キャラに、素晴らしい表現をする声優さん達には頭が上がりませ。"
  },
  {
    "id": 24,
    "text": "いつも素敵なイベントを作って、ありがとうござい。"
  },
  {
    "id": 25,
    "text": "、これからもお体に気を、頑張って。"
  },
  {
    "id": 26,
    "text": "一とうふとして応援していますといただきまし。"
  },
  {
    "id": 27,
    "text": "飯、ありがとうござい。"
  },
  {
    "id": 28,
    "text": "、イラストもね結構25だと珍しい色味というかなんかなんて言うん、"
  },
  {
    "id": 29,
    "text": "淡い色味は今までありました、なんか太陽光を浴びてる25を見れる、"
  },
  {
    "id": 30,
    "text": "、あんま外に出ない子達だからっていうのもあります、"
  },
  {
    "id": 31,
    "text": "日中の25って珍しいなって私は思っ、結構大体、、こういうタッチあんまりないなと思ったんです、"
  },
  {
    "id": 32,
    "text": "瑞希に限らず全員分良かったですから、特訓前も特訓後。"
  },
  {
    "id": 33,
    "text": "素晴らしい絵師がいるんだなと思いまし。"
  },
  {
    "id": 34,
    "text": "、本当ありがたいなと思ったんですけれど、、今回も、えイラスト制作チームから今回の衣装についてのコメントいただいておりますの、"
  },
  {
    "id": 35,
    "text": "、そちらも紹介させてもらえたらなと思い。"
  },
  {
    "id": 36,
    "text": "、コメントでもあります、純粋な明るさって珍しいですよねと言い。"
  },
  {
    "id": 37,
    "text": "、25に受け入れてもらえた瑞希が自分と同じように悩んでいる子、"
  },
  {
    "id": 38,
    "text": "、自分を好きになれない子の力になれるような服を作り、"
  },
  {
    "id": 39,
    "text": "服飾系の仕事に就きたいっていう自分の将来を考えるストーリーから着想を得、"
  },
  {
    "id": 40,
    "text": "、これから思い描いていく、やっと少しずつ見えてきた自分の未来というイメージを表現した、"
  },
  {
    "id": 41,
    "text": "、あえて要素が少ないシンプルかつ清楚なワンピースデザインにしてい。"
  },
  {
    "id": 42,
    "text": "ワンポイントとして瑞希の進級後のユニット衣装に用いてい、"
  },
  {
    "id": 43,
    "text": "、黄色いデイジーの刺繍を、、、自分らしさという、メッセージ性も乗せ、"
  },
  {
    "id": 44,
    "text": "今回の瑞希ならではのシンプルな衣装デザインとしてい。"
  },
  {
    "id": 45,
    "text": "、楽曲のゆったりと落ち着いた温かな印象や未来への淡い期待、"
  },
  {
    "id": 46,
    "text": "、、抱き始めた瑞希の心情表現を表すよう、淡く優しい色合いでまとめましたといただきまし。"
  },
  {
    "id": 47,
    "text": "確かに、全体的にも全員通して淡い色合いにはなっているなと思うんです、"
  },
  {
    "id": 48,
    "text": "そうなん、デイジーも、入ってるんだって皆さん、気づきまし?"
  },
  {
    "id": 49,
    "text": "デイジー入って。"
  },
  {
    "id": 50,
    "text": "、、デイジーってコメントがあります。"
  },
  {
    "id": 51,
    "text": "。"
  },
  {
    "id": 52,
    "text": "。"
  },
  {
    "id": 53,
    "text": "青い信号が印象的だっ。"
  },
  {
    "id": 54,
    "text": "確かに。"
  },
  {
    "id": 55,
    "text": "なんか瑞希って夏生まれ、8月20、、、お誕生日お。"
  },
  {
    "id": 56,
    "text": "こんな雑で言うつもりはなかった、誕生日おめでとうなんです、"
  },
  {
    "id": 57,
    "text": "夏だ、夏っぽいイラストって今まで結構そこまで多い方ではない子だなと私は思っていてだから、"
  },
  {
    "id": 58,
    "text": "なんか長袖だったりと、こう肌を覆ってる服が多かったりとかするなと私は思ってたんです、"
  },
  {
    "id": 59,
    "text": "、Tシャツとかありました、そういうの。"
  },
  {
    "id": 60,
    "text": "その中で結構爽やか、こう一瞬見ただけで夏だなって感じられるイラストを見れるのは嬉しいなって私は思いました。"
  },
  {
    "id": 61,
    "text": "、ということ、それでは、、カードイラストを実際に見ながらお話ししていけたらと思い。"
  },
  {
    "id": 62,
    "text": "これ今モニターに私映ってるよ、みんなのモニターに。"
  },
  {
    "id": 63,
    "text": "、信じてい。"
  },
  {
    "id": 64,
    "text": "では、瑞希から、特訓。"
  },
  {
    "id": 65,
    "text": "。"
  },
  {
    "id": 66,
    "text": "このねイラスト。"
  },
  {
    "id": 67,
    "text": "、お姉ちゃんがすごい嬉しそうににこにこ瑞希を見てるっていうのがお正月のイベントで、"
  },
  {
    "id": 68,
    "text": "、幼い頃の瑞希にリボンを贈った佑希さんとすごく重なるなと思ってい、"
  },
  {
    "id": 69,
    "text": "でどうかなって見せてるこの瑞希の表情がめちゃくちゃいいんです。"
  },
  {
    "id": 70,
    "text": "特訓前とは思えないよ。"
  },
  {
    "id": 71,
    "text": "本当。"
  },
  {
    "id": 72,
    "text": "この空間が私は大好き。"
  },
  {
    "id": 73,
    "text": "これ、映ってん、後ろに映ってのがトルソーですけれど、"
  },
  {
    "id": 74,
    "text": "。"
  },
  {
    "id": 75,
    "text": "ということ、特訓後も見ていき。"
  },
  {
    "id": 76,
    "text": "。"
  },
  {
    "id": 77,
    "text": "。"
  },
  {
    "id": 78,
    "text": "非常に"
  },
  {
    "id": 79,
    "text": "結構瑞希にとって蝶々だっ、リボンだったりっていうのはすごく象徴的になってるなと思ってたんです、"
  }
]

response_parts.content:
{
  "response": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "translated": "So, from here, I'd like to talk about the illustrations."
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "translated": "I'll start by reading a message."
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "translated": "This one is from Meshi."
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "translated": "Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "translated": "\"Hello, Sato-san.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "translated": "\"I'm always having a great time playing ProSeka.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "translated": "\"The 4-star illustrations this time, especially Mizuki's, were so good that I went all out on the gacha...\""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "translated": "\"...and I managed to get them!\""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "translated": "\"Just like in 'Secret Distance' or 'Our Escape to the Unknown'...\""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "translated": "\"'Michi wa Izuko'...\""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "translated": "\"...the post-trained illustration features Mizuki in a space with a torso.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "translated": "\"A torso is like a mannequin for clothes, which often appears in Mizuki's art.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "translated": "It's right here..."
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "translated": "..."
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "translated": "Right here."
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "translated": "This is called a torso."
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "translated": "\"Reaching out to an unbinding tomorrow... the torso.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "translated": "\"It's an illustration with Mizuki in a space filled with torsos.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "translated": "\"The torso space usually represented Mizuki's dark feelings,\""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "translated": "\"but this time, they're looking forward after feeling the warmth of family and friends.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "translated": "\"Seeing the space reflect Mizuki's bright and cheerful state of mind,\""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "translated": "\"I was so happy to see how much their heart has changed.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "translated": "\"I can't thank the staff enough for creating such a wonderful scenario,\""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "translated": "\"and the voice actors for giving the characters such depth and expression.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "translated": "\"Thank you for always creating such wonderful events.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "translated": "\"Please take care of yourselves and keep up the good work.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "translated": "\"I'll be rooting for you as a fellow Toufu,\" they wrote."
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "translated": "Meshi, thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "translated": "The colors in these illustrations are quite rare for Niigo."
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "translated": "We've had pale colors before, but seeing Niigo bathed in sunlight..."
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "translated": "Well, they don't really go outside much."
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "translated": "Seeing Niigo during the day is rare, and I felt this specific art style was quite unique."
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "translated": "Everyone's cards were great, not just Mizuki's, both pre-trained and post-trained."
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "translated": "It makes me realize what amazing artists we have."
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "translated": "I'm really grateful. We also received comments from the illustration team about the outfits,"
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "translated": "so I'd like to share those as well."
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "translated": "They mentioned that \"pure brightness\" is quite rare for them."
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "translated": "\"The story was inspired by Mizuki, who was accepted by Niigo, wanting to help others who have similar worries...\""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "translated": "\"...or who can't love themselves, by making clothes for them.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "translated": "\"It also draws from the story of Mizuki thinking about their future career in fashion.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "translated": "\"To express the image of a future they've finally started to see,\""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "translated": "\"we chose a simple and pure one-piece design with few elements.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "translated": "\"As a highlight, we included the yellow daisy embroidery used in Mizuki's new unit costume...\""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "translated": "\"...to convey the message of 'being yourself'.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "translated": "\"This resulted in a simple outfit design unique to Mizuki.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "translated": "\"To match the song's calm, warm impression and Mizuki's faint hope for the future,\""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "translated": "\"we used a palette of soft, gentle colors,\" they said."
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "translated": "It's true, everyone's cards have a very soft color scheme this time."
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "translated": "And did everyone notice the daisy? Did you see it?"
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "translated": "There's a daisy in there."
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "translated": "I see comments about the daisy now."
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "translated": "..."
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "translated": "..."
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "translated": "\"The blue traffic light was striking.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "translated": "That's true."
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "translated": "Mizuki was born in summer, on August 2... Happy Birthday!"
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "translated": "I didn't mean to say it so casually, but Happy Birthday."
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "translated": "Since it's summer, I feel like Mizuki hasn't had many summer-like illustrations until now."
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "translated": "They usually wear long sleeves or clothes that cover their skin."
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "translated": "Though there have been T-shirts and things like that."
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "translated": "So, seeing an illustration that feels like summer the moment you look at it is really nice."
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "translated": "With that said, let's take a look at the card illustrations together."
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "translated": "I'm on the monitor right now. On everyone's monitor."
    },
    {
      "id": 63,
      "translated": "I believe so, anyway."
    },
    {
      "id": 64,
      "translated": "Let's start with Mizuki's pre-trained card."
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
      "translated": "..."
    },
    {
      "id": 66,
      "translated": "This illustration..."
    },
    {
      "id": 67,
      "translated": "Their sister is looking at Mizuki with such a happy smile. In the New Year's event,"
    },
    {
      "id": 68,
      "translated": "it really reminds me of Yuuki-san giving a ribbon to a young Mizuki."
    },
    {
      "id": 69,
      "translated": "And Mizuki's expression while showing her the outfit is just wonderful."
    },
    {
      "id": 70,
